snippet.title: The Jim's Nightmare | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
After a long time. finally I am excited to show you the official trailer of The Jim's Nightmare. Make sure you like and subscribe and tell me your opinion in comment section blow!

Look at the game page (we may go on steam soon):
kasragamestudio.itch.io/jim-nightmar

Also you may like to see my team works as well:
digital art: www.artstation.com/alicanbagbekart
pixel art: www.pixilart.com/potatus
music: www.tqfproduction.com
vc actor: aaronkeysor.com
vc actress: www.kristina-rothe.com
